org.mcm.sws.process
Class Activity

java.lang.Object
  org.mcm.sws.process.Activity
Direct Known Subclasses:
AtomicActivity, CompoundActivity, GoalActivity, Process, Switch
public abstract class Activity
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract superclass of Activities. An activity is an executable element of a process. The semantic of activities is derived from UML activities in UML activity diagrams.

Author:
Joachim Peer
